I’ve also been sent loads of other goodies like a L.O.L. Surprise! mug, hot chocolate, sweets and my absolute fav marshmallows!
 
Make sure you check out L.O.L. Surprise! range on @bootsuk – the perfect gifts for treating yourself or someone special this Christmas.
